import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Home from './pages/Home'
import News from './pages/News'

function RoutesSite() {
return(
    <BrowserRouter>
        <Routes>
            <Route path='/' element={Home} />
            <Route path='News' element={News} />
        </Routes>   
    </BrowserRouter>
)
}

export default RoutesSite
